Fire & Freez

A multiplayer hide-and-seek adventure where every match is a race to uncover hidden treasures.


🔥❄️ Fire & Freez

Fire & Freez is a real-time multiplayer game that combines the excitement of Hide & Seek, Treasure Hunting, and Elemental Powers into one immersive experience.

Players enter a vibrant virtual world where survival depends on strategy, teamwork, exploration, and deception. Every match presents new challenges as treasures spawn at random locations, encouraging players to adapt their tactics and outsmart their opponents.

Whether you're hiding in plain sight, searching for valuable treasures, or using powerful Fire and Freeze abilities, no two games are ever the same.